IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CLAIMENGINE.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       EXEC SQL BEGIN DECLARE SECTION END-EXEC.
       01 DB-CLAIM-ID      PIC 9(6).
       01 DB-POLICY-ID     PIC 9(6).
       01 DB-AMOUNT        PIC 9(7)V99.
       EXEC SQL END DECLARE SECTION END-EXEC.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "CLAIM ENGINE: PROCESSING CLAIM".

           DISPLAY "CLAIM ID: " DB-CLAIM-ID " FOR POLICY: " DB-POLICY-ID.
           DISPLAY "AMOUNT  : " DB-AMOUNT.

           GOBACK.